63c5ccab4abc992e8c72b2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222349%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMax%20Levchin%2C%20Affirm's%20CEO%2C%20said%20AI%20chatbots%20could%20save%20the%20company%20money%20in%20one%20to%20three%20years.%3Cp%3EGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAffirm%20is%20investing%20heavily%20in%20AI-powered%20chatbots%20to%20cater%20to%20Gen%20Z's%20phone%20aversion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20chatbots%20are%20expected%20to%20replace%2020-30%25%20of%20customer%20service%20agents%20by%202026%2C%20according%20to%20Gartner.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20the%20potential%20savings%20and%20efficiency%2C%20AI%20customer%20service%20has%20seen%20limited%20adoption.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20hates%20talking%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20so%20companies%20like%20the%20%249.7%20billion%20buy-now%2C%20pay-later%20giant%20Affirm%20are%20betting%20big%20on%20AI-powered%20chatbots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bots%20let%20voice-averse%20customers%20solve%20problems%20online%2C%20Affirm%20CEO%20Max%20Levchin%20said%20on%20an%20earnings%20call%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20investing%20really%20heavily%20in%20this%20idea%20that%20Gen%20Z%20consumers%20really%20love%20chatting%20versus%20calling%20and%20they%20have%20no%20problem%20chatting%20with%20an%20Al%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20Al%20is%20intelligent%2C%26quot%3B%20Levchin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffirm%20uses%20chatbots%20to%20solve%20fast%20queries%2C%20like%20policy%20questions%2C%20and%20then%20real%20people%20take%20over%20for%20more%20complicated%20cases%2C%20Levchin%20said.%20The%20PayPal%20alumnus%20said%20chatbots%20are%20helping%20Affirm%20scale%20its%20customer%20service%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffirm%20built%20an%20AI-based%20assistant%20and%20tested%20it%20in%20the%20last%20quarter.%20Less%20than%2040%25%20of%20users%20needed%20to%20speak%20with%20a%20human%20after%20using%20the%20bot%2C%20Levchin%20wrote%20in%20a%20shareholder%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20has%20yet%20to%20lose%20their%20job%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20robot%20at%20a%20firm%2C%20so%20that's%20not%20a%20short-term%20cost%20saving%2C%26quot%3B%20Levchin%20said%20on%20Wednesday's%20call%2C%20adding%20that%20AI%20could%20save%20the%20company%20money%20over%20the%20next%20one%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20research%20firm%20Gartner%20estimated%20last%20year%20that%20by%202026%2C%20AI%20will%20replace%2020-30%25%20of%20customer%20service%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nascent%20technology%20is%20already%20having%20a%20big%20bottom-line%20impact%20for%20some%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeb%20Cupp%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Microsoft%20Americas%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavos-global-elite-saying-about-ai-behind-closed-doors-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20panel%20discussion%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Davos%20in%20January%20that%20the%20software%20giant%20saved%20%24100%20million%20in%20its%20customer-service%20operation%20by%20implementing%20AI.%20Microsoft%20also%20sells%20AI-powered%20customer%20service%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMihir%20Shukla%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Automation%20Anywhere%2C%20said%20at%20Davos%20that%20the%20company%20cut%20customer-service%20costs%20by%2040%25%20while%20seeing%20improved%20performance%20since%20introducing%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20customer%20service%20hasn't%20been%20a%20panacea%20for%20all%20businesses%2C%20though.%20People%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcar-dealership-chevrolet-chatbot-chatgpt-pranks-chevy-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etricked%20and%20hacked%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20car%20dealership's%20customer%20service%20AI%20in%20December%2C%20and%20in%20January%2C%20a%20UK%20mail%20service's%20bot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparcel-delivery-firm-pr-nightmare-ai-chatbot-cusses-mocked-company-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswore%20at%20