had%20no%20other%20complaint.%20No%20rape%20happened.%20She%20(Piyali)%20made%20us%20sign%20on%20a%20blank%20sheet%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20later%20came%20to%20know%20that%20she%20is%20on%20the%20list%20of%20women%20who%20alleged%20rape%20by%20local%20Trinamool%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20daughters-in-law%20accused%20Piyali%20of%20defaming%20Sandeshkhali.%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20an%20outsider%2C%20she%20has%20come%20from%20somewhere%20else%20and%20talks%20big.%20We%20don't%20know%20how%20she%20has%20information%20about%20everyone%20here.%20Initially%2C%20she%20would%20just%20take%20part%20in%20the%20protests%20here.%20We%20later%20came%20to%20know%20she%20is%20with%20the%20BJP.%20She%20should%20be%20punished%20for%20lying%20to%20us%20and%20trapping%20us.%20I'm%20sure%20more%20people%20were%20deceived%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%C2%A0The%20woman%20and%20her%20family%20said%20they%20are%20now%20receiving%20threats%20for%20coming%20out%20against%20Piyali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20on%20the%20backfoot%20after%20local%20party%20leaders%20were%20accused%20of%20rape%2C%20land%20grab%20and%20extortion%2C%20has%20latched%20on%20to%20the%20woman's%20allegations%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20cooking%20up%20stories%20to%20malign%20the%20ruling%20party%20for%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20MP%20Sushmita%20Dev%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20threatening%20the%20%26quot%3Bcourageous%20women%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20for%20daring%20to%20speak%20out%20against%20them%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20longer%20will%20this%20party%20persist%20in%20spinning%20webs%20of%20deceit%2C%20shamelessly%20trampling%20on%20the%20dignity%20of%20our%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20for%20their%20own%20political%20greed%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20hit%20back%2C%20describing%20Trinamool's%20allegations%20as%20a%20damage%20control%20exercise%20that%20has%20come%20too%20late.%20Party%20spokesperson%20Priyanka%20Tibrewal%20said%20the%20Trinamool%20must%20understand%20that%20there%20is%20no%20use%20crying%20over%20spilt%20milk.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20Trinamool%20responding%20now%3F%20Why%20were%20they%20quiet%20for%20two-three%20months.%20They%20earlier%20said%20the%20women%20(of%20Sandeshkhali)%20were%20lying%2C%20now%20they%20are%20saying%20they%20were%20made%20to%20lie.%20Whatever%20damage%20had%20to%20happen%20has%20happened.%20There%20is%20no%20smoke%20without%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20now%20registered%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20against%20several%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20levelling%20fabricated%20allegations%20in%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nondescript%20island%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20made%20headlines%20in%20February%20when%20local%20residents%20accused%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20aides%20of%20harassing%20them.%20Shahjahan%2C%20now%20expelled%20by%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20was%20arrested%20after%20he%20was%20on%20the%20run%20for%20over%20a%20month%20in%20a%20case%20relating%20to%20a%20mob%20attack%20on%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officials%20probing%20him.%20He%20is%20now%20in%20the%20CBI's%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shocking%20twist%20in%20the%20Sandeskhali%20row%20last%20week%2C%20a%20video%20of%20a%20local%20BJP%20leader%20started%20doing%20the%20rounds.%20The%20video%20showed%20Gangadhar%20Koyal%20purportedly%20admitting%20that%20no%20rapes%20or%20sexual%20harassment%20took%20place%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20that%20women%20were%20convinced%20to%20file%20such%20complaints%20at%20the%20directions%20of%20Mr%20Adhikari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20leader%20in%20the%20video%20have%20claimed%20that%20th