0you%20to%20direct%20the%20appropriate%20authority%20to%20immediately%20call%20for%20a%20floor%20test%20to%20determine%20majority%20of%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chautala's%20letter%20to%20the%20Governor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20for%20a%20floor%20test%20stems%20from%20the%20recent%20switch%20of%20three%20Independent%20MLAs%20from%20the%20BJP%20faction%20to%20the%20Congress%20faction.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20MLAs%20Sombir%20Sangwan%20(representing%20Dadri)%2C%20Randhir%20Singh%20Gollen%20(from%20Pundri)%2C%20and%20Dharampal%20Gonder%20(of%20Nilokheri)%20declared%20their%20intention%20to%20cut%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%20administration%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20held%20in%20Rohtak.%20They%20were%20joined%20by%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20and%20Udai%20Bhan%2C%20the%20state%20Congress%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chautala%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%20which%20is%20a%20former%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20did%20not%20mince%20words%20in%20expressing%20his%20party's%20readiness%20to%20throw%20its%20weight%20behind%20an%20alternative%20government%2C%20signalling%20a%20potential%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20that%20was%20formed%20two%20months%20back%20is%20now%20in%20the%20minority%20because%20two%20of%20the%20MLAs%20who%20supported%20them%20-%20one%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20other%20an%20Independent%20MLA%20-%20have%20resigned.%20Three%20Independent%20MLAs%20who%20were%20supporting%20them%20have%20withdrawn%20their%20support%20and%20have%20written%20to%20the%20Governor.%20JJP%20has%20clearly%20said%20that%20if%20a%20No%20Confidence%20Motion%20is%20brought%20against%20this%20government%2C%20we%20will%20support%20the%20motion%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chautala%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20also%20written%20to%20the%20Governor%20about%20it.%20Now%2C%20Congress%20has%20to%20take%20this%20step%20(seeking%20a%20Floor%20Test).%20The%20Governor%20has%20the%20power%20to%20order%20a%20Floor%20Test%20to%20see%20if%20the%20Government%20has%20the%20strength%20and%20if%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20majority%20immediately%20implement%20President's%20Rule%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20Assembly%2C%20with%2090%20seats%2C%20is%20currently%20occupied%20by%2088%20members%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20mark%20at%2045.%20BJP%20commands%2040%20MLAs%20supported%20by%20three%20out%20of%20six%20independent%20candidates%2C%20meaning%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20is%20short%20of%20two%20MLAs%20to%20hit%20the%20majority.%20The%20Congress%20party%20boasts%2030%20MLAs%20with%20its%20count%20bolstered%20by%20three%20independent%20candidates.%20Should%20the%20JJP%20lend%20its%20support%2C%20the%20Congress's%20tally%20would%20rise%20to%2043%20MLAs.%20This%20scenario%20leaves%20two%20MLAs%20unaligned-one%20from%20the%20Haryana%20Lokhit%20Party%20and%20the%20other%20from%20the%20INLD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAftab%20Ahmed%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20deputy%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Haryana%20assembly%2C%20has%20asked%20for%20time%20to%20meet%20the%20Governor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715239560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fc0cvak3g_dushyant-chautala-1200_625x300_17_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fex-bjp-ally-dushyant-chautala-writes-to-haryana-governor-seeks-floor-test-5623367%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Haryana%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20ally%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Governor%2C%20demanding%20a%20floor%20test%20in%20the%20state%20assembly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fex-bjp-ally-dushyant-chautala-writes-to-haryana-governor-seeks-floor-test-5623367%22%2C%22cdnA