sful%20industrialist%20and%20also%20the%20co-owner%20of%20ISL%20runner-up%20Mohun%20Bagan%20Super%20Giant%2C%20was%20not%20a%20happy%20man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Goenka%20had%20bid%20over%20Rs%207000%20crore%20to%20buy%20LSG%20franchise%20in%20IPL.%20According%20to%20several%20reports%2C%20Goenka%20will%20pay%20BCCI%20a%20franchise%20of%20Rs%207090%20crore%20over%2010%20years.%20With%20him%20ready%20to%20shell%20out%20such%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20money%2C%20the%20attachment%20that%20Goenka%20has%20with%20the%20team%20is%20very%20apparent.%20His%20franchise%20has%20done%20well%20too%20in%20the%20past%2C%20reaching%20the%20playoffs%20in%20its%20first%20two%20years%20under%20KL%20Rahul's%20captaincy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20however%2C%20things%20seemed%20to%20be%20different.%20Though%20playoffs%20hopes%20are%20not%20lost%2C%20LSG%20are%20in%20a%20tricky%20spot.%20The%20team%20is%20sixth%20among%2010%20teams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%2010-wicket%20thrashing%20to%20SRH%20has%20added%20to%20the%20woes.%20And%20it%20seemed%2C%20it%20was%20too%20much%20for%20Goenka%20to%20handle.%20Throughout%20the%20match%2C%20Goenka%20could%20be%20seen%20following%20the%20match%20quite%20closely.%20Following%20the%20loss%2C%20however%2C%20emotion%20seemed%20to%20take%20control.%20Even%20the%20broadcaster%20could%20not%20help%20but%20term%20the%20interaction%20between%20Goenka%20and%20Rahul%20as%20%26quot%3Banimated%20reaction%20from%20LSG%20camp%26quot%3B.%20Even%20LSG%20coach%20and%20Australia%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Justin%20Langer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F267-justin-langer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJustin%20Langer%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20not%20spared%20either%2C%20as%20Goenka%20seemed%20to%20given%20him%20an%20earful%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20through%20this%20while%2C%20Rahul%20and%20Langer%2C%20stayed%20calm%20and%20took%20it%20all%20in.%20Rarely%20has%20such%20a%20scene%20been%20telecast%20on%20national%20television.%20But%2C%20can%20the%20readers%20vouch%20and%20say%20such%20incidents%20don't%20happen%20every%20day%20in%20boardrooms%20and%20corporate%20houses%3F%20Does%20this%20win%20at%20all%20cost%20mentality%20not%20play%20out%20daily%20at%20all%20work%20place%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20recently%2C%20two%20videos%20went%20viral%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20where%20officers%20of%20Bandhan%20Bank%20and%20Canara%20Bank%20can%20be%20seen%20reprimanding%20their%20junior%20employees%20using%20foul%20language%20over%20failing%20to%20meet%20targets.%20%C2%A0A%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20similar%20such%20incident%20happened%20in%20another%20bank%20and%20the%20foul-mouthing%20official%20was%20suspended.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoenka's%20case%20got%20more%20highlighted%20as%20he%20is%20a%20celebrated%20name.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20he%20may%20have%20momentarily%20forgotten%20that%20with%20the%20plethora%20of%20cameras%20on%20ground%2C%20nothing%20stays%20hidden.%20He%20has%20every%20right%20to%20feel%20bad%20about%20his%20team's%20loss%2C%20but%20to%20vent%20out%20his%20frustration%20at%20his%20captain%20on%20cricket%20matters%2C%20for%20which%20he%20has%20hired%20specialist%20support%20staff%2C%20was%20that%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20for%20every%20serious%20discussion%2C%20there%20is%20a%20thing%20called%20'closed%20door%20meeting'%2C%20something%20which%20the%20official%20broadcaster's%20also%20mentioned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaybe%20he%20could%20have%20taken%20a%20cue%20from%20how%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Rides%20co-owner%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20reacted%20after%20his%20side's%20loss%20to%20Rajasthan%20Royals.%20In%20a%20video%2C%20which%20went%20viral%2C%20SRK%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20it's%20a%20very%20proud%20day.%20The%20way%20we%20played%3B%20all%20of%20us.%20I%20won't%20take%20individual%20names%3B%20that's%20been%20done.%20Don't%20feel%20down%2C%20GG.%20We%20will%20all%20bounce%20back.%20It's%20God's%20plan%20for%20today%2C%20as%20Rinku%20says.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20what%20we%20would%20like%20them%20to%20do.%20We'll%20be%20back%20with%20more%20and%20better%2C%20God%20willing.%20Thank%20you%2C%20everyone%2C%20and%20may%20God%20bless%20all.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20other%20owners%20follow%20SRK's%20line%3F%20It's%20completely%20up%20to%20them%2C%20ultimately%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20spend%20the%20money%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20cash-rich%20private%20league%20-%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715239020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fptpm0828_b_625x300_09_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Flsg-owner-sanjiv-goenkas-on-camera-outburst-at-kl-rahul-just-emotion-or-reflection-of-broader-toxic-culture-5623450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20owner%20Sanjiv%20Goenka%20had%20a%20fiery%20conversation%20with%20skipper%20KL%20Rahul%20following%20their%20big%20loss%20against%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Farak%20toh%20pada%20hai'%3A%20Akram%20on%20MI%20crashing%20out%20of%20IPL%20playoff%20race%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715239006000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109972804%2Cimgsize-68924.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Flast-minute-mein-jo-usse-farak-toh-pada-hain-wasim-akram-offers-insights-as-mumbai-indians-crash-out-of-ipl-playoff-race%2Farticleshow%2F109971739.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20five-time%20IPL%20champions%2C%20have%20been%20eliminated%20from%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20playoffs%2C%20their%20fate%20sealed%20after%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20thumped%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants.%20MI%20have%20registered%20onl