r%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Ohio%2C%20the%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20New%20York%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20New%20York%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Banguished%26quot%3B%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20death%20of%20Mohammed%20Abdul%20Arfath%20and%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20local%20authorities%20to%20ensure%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnguished%20to%20learn%20that%20Mr.%20Mohammed%20Abdul%20Arfath%2C%20for%20whom%20search%20operation%20was%20underway%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20Cleveland%2C%20Ohio.%20Our%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20Mr%20Mohammed%20Arfath's%20family%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20New%20York%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArafat%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20went%20to%20the%20US%20for%20his%20Master's%20degree%20in%20IT%20from%20Cleveland%20University%20in%20May%202023%20but%20had%20been%20missing%20since%20March%207%20this%20year.%20His%20father%2C%20Mohd%20Saleem%2C%20said%20that%20after%20ten%20days%2C%20they%20received%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20an%20unidentified%20person%20who%20claimed%20Arafat%20had%20been%20kidnapped%20and%20demanded%20a%20USD%201200%20ransom%20for%20his%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20Indian%20community%20has%20seen%20a%20rise%20in%20such%20tragedies.%20In%20April%2C%20Uma%20Satya%20Sai%20Gadde%2C%20an%20Indian%20student%20in%20Cleveland%2C%20Ohio%2C%20died%20and%20a%20police%20investigation%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20February%2C%20an%20Indian%20student%20faced%20a%20brutal%20attack%20in%20Chicago.%20Following%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20Indian%20Consulate%20in%20Chicago%20stated%20that%20it%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20victim%2C%20Syed%20Mazahir%20Ali%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20wife%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20n