en%20moved%20for%20the%20project%2C%20though%20UK-based%20human%20rights%20group%20ALQST%20estimates%20the%20number%20to%20be%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20shared%20satellite%20data%20claiming%20that%20three%20villages%20-%20al-Khuraybah%2C%20Sharma%20and%20Gayal%20-%20were%20demolished%20for%20the%20project.%20These%20villages%20were%20inhabited%20by%20the%20Huwaitat%20tribe%2C%20which%20has%20been%20dubbed%20a%20group%20of%20%26quot%3Brebels%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20government%20order%2C%20said%20Col%20Alenezi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeom%20is%20the%20centrepiece%20of%20Mohamed%20Bin%20Salman's%20ideas.%20That's%20why%20he%20was%20so%20brutal%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20Huwaitat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%20He%20now%20lives%20in%20the%20UK%20foe%20his%20own%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20futuristic%20megacity%20is%20touted%20to%20be%2033%20times%20the%20size%20of%20New%20York%2C%20with%20an%20area%20of%2026%2C500%20km%20square%20extending%20along%20the%20Aqaba%20Gulf%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20Red%20Sea%20coastline.%20The%20name%20Neom%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20Greek%20term%20Neo%20and%20Arabic%20word%20for%20%26quot%3Bfuture%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20(WSJ)%20said%20in%202022%20that%20MBS%20has%20ordered%20workers%20to%20construct%2010%20palaces%2C%20each%20bigger%20than%20a%20football%20field.%20The%20outlet%20reviewed%20the%20project's%20plan%2C%20which%20showed%20that%20the%20houses%20could%20list%20at%20up%20to%20%24400%20million%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715235300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fud9n83do_saudi-megacity-neom-afp_625x300_29_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-forces-told-to-kill-to-clear-land-for-futuristic-city-neom-report-5623040%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Neom%20is%20touted%20to%20be%2033%20times%20the%20size%20of%20New%20York%2C%20with%20an%20area%20of%2026%2C500%20km%20s