rogramme.%20Eight%20years%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frohith-vemula-suicide-case-family-to-challenge-polices-closure-report-5583784%5C%22%3Ethe%20Telangana%20police%20claim%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Rohith%20was%20not%20Dalit%20and%20that%20it%20was%20likely%20the%20fear%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Breal%20caste%26quot%3B%20being%20revealed%20that%20led%20him%20to%20suicide.%20At%20the%20core%20of%20this%20claim%20are%20some%20formalities%20of%20law%20and%20policy%20that%20must%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%20status%20is%20legally%20determined%20by%20ancestry.%20More%20specifically%2C%20the%20bloodlines%20of%20men%20are%20the%20carriages%20of%20caste.%20That%20is%20to%20say%2C%20formal%20legal%20procedures%20require%20the%20SC%20certification%20of%20a%20father%20to%20grant%20an%20SC%20certificate%20to%20a%20child.%20This%20patriarchal%20character%20of%20law%20and%20policy%20has%20been%20contested%20in%20courts.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20judicial%20interventions%2C%20a%20mother's%20SC%20certification%20can%20be%20admitted%20for%20certifying%20a%20child's%20SC%20status.%20But%20this%20is%20an%20exception%2C%20not%20a%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Process%20Of%20Humiliation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESC%20certifications%20at%20local%20governance%20levels%20have%20also%20changed%20over%20time.%20Plus%2C%20sometimes%2C%20these%20certifications%20can%20be%20outcomes%20of%20discretionary%20functions%20of%20power.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20SC%20certifications%20could%20be%20granted%20based%20on%20supporting%20statements%20of%20gazetted%20government%20officers%20and%20ordinary%20neighbours%20too.%20In%20cases%20where%20neither%20parent%20has%20a%20formal%20caste%20certificate%2C%20that%20ordeal%20is%20worse%20as%20an%20individual%C2%A0-%C2%A0%20especially%20interstate%20migrant%20workers%C2%A0-%20runs%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20trying%20to%20get%20their%20caste%20identity%20certified.%20All%20such%20processes%20inadvertently%20end%20up%20imposing%20varying%20degrees%20of%20humiliation%20upon%20those%20who%20want%20to%20obtain%20SC%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-name-is-rohith-vemula-i-am-a-dalit-he-said-in-video-days-before-he-died-1475243%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%20'My%20Name%20Is%20Rohith%20Vemula.%20I%20Am%20A%20Dalit%2C'%20He%20Said%20In%20Video%20Days%20Before%20He%20Died%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20kind%20of%20humiliation%20has%20been%20playing%20out%20openly%20for%20anyone%20to%20see%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Rohith%20Vemula%20and%20his%20mother%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fshows%2Findia-matters%2Frohith-vemula-his-mother-s-son-445670%5C%22%3ERadhika%20Vemula%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Born%20to%20SC%20Mala%20parents%2C%20Radhika%20was%20adopted%20by%20an%20Other%20Backward%20Class%20(OBC)%20Vaddera%20woman%2C%20and%20later%2C%20she%20married%20a%20Vaddera%20man.%20Despite%20the%20two%20legalities%20-%20adoption%20and%20marriage%20-%20Radhika%20could%20retain%20her%20SC%20status%20because%20of%20the%20bloodline%20of%20her%20SC%20Mala%20father.%20Furthermore%2C%20Radhika%20later%20returned%20to%20her%20SC%20community%20after%20leaving%20her%20OBC%20husband.%20Patriarchy%20is%20so%20deeply%20entrenched%20in%20law%20and%20policy%20that%20Rohith%20Vemula's%20caste%20is%20now%20determined%20by%20the%20caste%20of%20an%20absent%20OBC%20father%2C%20not%20his%20present%20SC%20mother.%20Ultimately%2C%20legality%20here%20appears%20to%20operate%20as%20an%20informal%20tool%20for%20imposing%20humiliation%20and%20adding%20insult%20to%20injury%20at%20mass%20levels%20of%20Dalit%20consciousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20%3Cem%3ESujata%20%3C%2Fem%3EStory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBimal%20Roy's%20famous%20movie%20%3Cem%3ESujata%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1959)%20is%20something%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20current%20fanciful%20s