uld%20be%20coming.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-crisis-crash-fed-economy-inflation-rates-sternlicht-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBillionaire%20Barry%20Sternlicht%3C%2Fa%3E%20offered%20an%20ominous%20prediction%20about%20America's%20regional%20banks%20amid%20a%20coming%20commercial%20real%20estate%20reckoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Starwood%20Capital%20Group%20CEO%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhdRvu0sI3zM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20thinks%20real%20estate's%20primary%20lenders%20%E2%80%94%20regional%20and%20community%20banks%20%E2%80%94%20could%20soon%20be%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20high%20interest%20rates%20and%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20see%20a%20regional%20bank%20fail%20every%20day%2C%20or%20not%20%E2%80%94%20every%20week%2C%20maybe%20two%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20Sternlicht%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20more%20than%204%2C000%20regional%20and%20community%20banks%20throughout%20the%20US%2C%20many%20of%20which%20may%20not%20have%20the%20cash%20flow%20to%20handle%20major%20loan%20losses%20on%20real%20estate%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProblems%20have%20been%20pummeling%20the%20entirety%20of%20the%20real%20estate%20sector%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-big-trouble-crash-bank-crisis-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercial%20real%20estate%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20been%20struggling%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20remote%20and%20hybrid%20work%2C%20leading%20to%20more%20and%20more%20vacancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESternlicht%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarry-sternlicht-recession-us-economy-outlook-real-estate-storm-fed-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eringing%20the%20warning%20bells%20%3C%2Fa%3