0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fgilmoreag_%2Fstatus%2F1786069451286237682%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echarged%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20their%20stay-in%20cleaning%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20clean%20the%20place%20yourself%20AND%20pay%20for%20cleaning%20fee%2C%20you've%20got%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20host%20one-on-one%2C%20and%20prices%20are%20no%20longer%20cheaper%20than%20hotels%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20user%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FAirBnB%2Fcomments%2F14en4yi%2Fis_airbnb_even_worth_it_anymore%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Reddit.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20actual%20point%20of%20Airbnb%20anymore%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-ceo-hosts-lower-prices-competitive-hotels-brian-chesky-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20CEO%20addressed%20the%20shifting%20perception%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Airbnb's%20costs%20in%20the%20company's%20first-quarter%20earnings%20call%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20announced%20initiatives%20to%20improve%20the%20pricing%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%2C%20you%20know%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20concern%20about%20Airbnb%20prices%20increasing%2C%26quot%3B%20Chesky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20one%20initiative%20to%20increase%20transparency%20around%20prices%20was%20the%20added%20option%20to%20view%20the%20total%20price%20of%20a%20listing%20before%20taxes.%20Before%20booking%2C%20users%20can%20see%20the%20full%20breakdown%20of%20service%20fees%2C%20discounts%2C%20and%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Chesky%2C%20the%20added%20feature%20has%20led%20customers%20to%20choose%20the%20best%20total%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirbnb%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airbnb.com.sg%2Fresources%2Fhosting-homes%2Fa%2Fnew-pricing-tool-compares-similar-listings-nearby-583%3F_set_bev_on_n