%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Kinnauri%20apples%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20ones%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20the%20apple%20growers%20never%20receive%20their%20fair%20share.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20get%20payment%20almost%2015%20to%2020%20days%20late%20or%20sometimes%20after%20six%20months%3B%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20nothing%20at%20all.%20Apples%20were%20sold%20for%20Rs%20300%20per%20kg%20in%20the%20market%20but%20the%20grower%20would%20get%20only%20Rs%2060%20%E2%80%93%20five%20times%20less%20than%20its%20market%20value.%20This%20corrupt%20system%20has%20been%20in%20practice%20for%2050%20to%2070%20years%2C%20and%20nobody%20voiced%20the%20problems%20of%20these%20small%20farmers.%20Despite%20this%2C%20farmers%20had%20been%20working%20with%20utmost%20honesty%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20heartbreaking%20for%20Ashish%20to%20see%20the%20market%20apathy%20for%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CGrowing%20crops%20is%20not%20a%20cakewalk%20and%20growing%20apples%20is%20certainly%20not%20easy.%20Usually%2C%20any%20plant%20requires%20three%20or%20four%20months%20of%20care%20but%20apples%20require%20a%20minimum%20of%20nine%20to%2010%20months%20of%20care.%20We%20only%20harvest%20once%20a%20year%20and%20look%20after%20the%20tree%20for%20the%20remaining%20months.%20You%E2%80%99ll%20see%20an%20apple%20farmer%20every%20day%20in%20the%20field%2C%20come%20what%20may%20%E2%80%94%20pest%20attacks%2C%20hailstorms%2C%20unseasonal%20rains%2C%20and%20snow.%20They%20nurture%20and%20protect%20them%20like%20a%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20farmer%20himself%2C%20Ashish%20decided%20it%20was%20high%20time%20to%20redirect%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20gold%20in%20them%20thar%20hills%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Ashish%20launched%20an%20online%20platform%20%E2%80%98Kayang%E2%80%99%20to%20end%20the%20woes%20of%20farmers%20and%20bring%20t