0I%20could%20not%20do%20a%20masters%20in%20farming.%20I%20was%20adamant%20and%20wanted%20to%20learn%20urban%20farming%20which%20is%20why%20I%20decided%20to%20look%20for%20colleges%20outside%20India.%20I%20found%20one%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20got%20admitted%20into%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20went%20beyond%20mere%20farming%3B%20it%20delved%20deeply%20into%20the%20nutrition%20we%20require.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20returned%2C%20I%20began%20teaching%20as%20a%20visiting%20faculty%20member%20at%20several%20colleges%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20Watching%20my%20students%20grow%20microgreens%20inspired%20me%20to%20try%20it%20out%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20previously%20her%20work%20and%20life%20got%20in%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20we%20were%20all%20confined%20to%20our%20homes%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20I%20had%20an%20empty%20guest%20room%2C%20which%20I%20converted%20into%20a%20space%20to%20grow%20microgreens%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20whole%20process%20very%20intriguing%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20take%20it%20up%20as%20a%20business.%20I%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20my%20own%20farm%20and%20grow%20microgreens%20commercially.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20Mali%20Greens%20in%202021.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20with%20growing%201%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20at%20home%20and%20now%20my%20farm%20can%20grow%2050%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20in%20one%20harvest%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Aditi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20microgreens%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFalling%20between%20the%20categories%20of%20a%20baby%20green%20and%20a%20sprout%2C%20microgreens%20are%20nutrition-packed%20herbs%20and%20vegetables.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EHealthline%3C%2Fem%3Earticle%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20often%20contain%20higher%20nutrient%20levels%20than%20more%20mature%20vegetable%20greens.%20This%20makes%20them%20a%20good%20addition%20to%20any%20diet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditi%20believes%20that%20India%20still%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306361%2Fwhy-is-makhana-expensive-lotus-seeds-fox-nuts-grown-in-bihar-gi-tagged-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20the%20superfood%3C%2Fa%3E%20microgreens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20am%20at%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20market%20or%20at%20pop-ups%20and%20am%20interacting%20with%20the%20people%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20unawareness%20among%20them.%20Including%20these%20little%20pockets%20of%20nutrition%20in%20your%20daily%20diet%20can%20really%20do%20wonders%20for%20your%20body.%20They%20contain%20large%20amounts%20of%20vitamins%20B%2C%20K%20and%20C%2C%20folic%20acid%2C%20magnesium%2C%20minerals%20and%20antioxidants%2C%20which%20have%20immense%20health%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20consume%2020-30%20gm%20of%20a%20microgreen%20vegetable%2C%20you%20are%20eating%20double%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20regular%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22She%20grows%20and%20sells%2050%20kgs%20of%20microgreens%20every%20month.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-