0that%20the%20delivery%20is%20fresh%20and%20natural.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20overproduce%20at%20all%2C%20we%20feed%20it%20to%20stray%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20the%20power-packed%20superfoods%20can%20come%20with%20a%20set%20of%20challenges.%20Talking%20about%20it%2C%20Aditi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20concept%20is%20still%20relatively%20new%2C%20there%20are%20not%20many%20resources%20available%20to%20set%20up%20a%20microgreen%20farm.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20racks%20to%20the%20boxes%2C%20sourcing%20raw%20materials%20was%20challenging.%20We%20repurposed%20trays%20for%20use%20in%20our%20setup.%20For%20the%20soil%2C%20I%20experimented%20with%20different%20combinations%20of%20soils%20and%20cocopeat%20to%20find%20the%20right%20mix%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20trial%20and%20error.%20There%20were%20no%20direct%20predecessors%20to%20learn%20from%2C%20so%20I%20relied%20on%20online%20resources%20and%20YouTube%20videos%20to%20understand%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20a%20balance%20between%20the%20demand%20and%20scaling%20the%20farm%20was%20another%20challenge%20that%20Aditi%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20tricky%20to%20develop%20a%20balance%20between%20demand%20and%20supply%20of%20the%20microgreen.%20We%20are%20still%20learning%20on%20the%20go%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20much%20we%20can%20do%20but%20learn%20from%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20mistakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20keep%20before%20starting%20a%20microgreens%20business%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Market%20your%20product%20before%20growing%20microgreens%2C%20Aditi%20advises.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20make%20people%20understand%20what%20they%20are%20and%20why%20they%20should%20consume%20it.%20Once%20you%20have%20found%20your%20market%2C%20you%20can%20start%20investing%20money%20into%20a%20farm