%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kavita%20proudly%20declares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20isn%E2%80%99t%20busy%20humming%20around%20her%20beloved%20flowers%2C%20Kavita%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20pottery%20studio.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20gives%20me%20great%20joy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20goes%20on%20to%20share%20an%20amusing%20story.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tamarind%20tree%20has%20been%20on%20the%20property%20for%20years%20now.%20And%20recently%20I%20had%20the%20pottery%20studio%20built%20in%20front%20of%20it.%20I%20have%20many%20guests%20who%20visit%20the%20studio%20for%20classes%2C%20and%20I%20am%20certain%20that%20this%20spike%20in%20human%20interaction%20in%20the%20past%20year%20has%20in%20some%20way%20influenced%20the%20tree.%20Because%20now%20it%20is%20giving%20us%20so%20much%20tamarind%2C%20much%20more%20than%20before!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20further%20fuels%20her%20theory%20that%20homes%20and%20nature%20also%20need%20company%20sometimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Parijaat%20Goa%20Homestay%2C%20food%20is%20always%20prepared%20fresh%20and%20the%20guests%20swear%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3Eshakshouka%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Epoie%20%3C%2Fem%3E(eggs%20poached%20in%20a%20flavourful%20sauce%20and%20eaten%20along%20with%20Goan%20bread)%2C%20%E2%81%A0%3Cem%3Eappam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20thin%20pancake)%20and%20stew%2C%20and%20their%20%3Cem%3E%E2%81%A0idli%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Esambhar%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Echutney.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nair%20family%20treats%20every%20guest%20like%20their%20own.%20Through%20the%20years%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20response%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321695%2Faamir-khanyari-turned-ancestral-land-into-traditional-kashmir-homestay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20homestay%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20seen%20has%20been%20a%20nod%20to%20Kavita%20and%20Manoj%E2%80%99s%20efforts.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20when%20we%20first%20saw%20this%20piece%2