ww.thebetterindia.com%2F330088%2Fkerala-architect-designer-anupa-kurian-renovates-century-old-ancestral-home-sustainable-upcycle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20house%20breathable%20and%20cooler%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20summer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20always%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20look%20back%20at%20our%20ancestors%20and%20how%20they%20used%20various%20techniques%20to%20deal%20with%20indoor%20heat.%20Evaporative%20cooling%20is%20a%20technique%20where%20you%20build%20an%20indoor%20water%20body%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%20a%20fountain%20to%20cool%20down%20the%20temperature%20inside%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20water%20body%20in%20the%20house%20can%20do%20wonders.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20can%20also%20cool%20down%20the%20air%20that%20passes%20through%20the%20home.%20This%20method%20is%20very%20effective%20in%20homes%20in%20the%20northern%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20where%20the%20humidity%20is%20relatively%20low%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrees%20and%20shade%20keep%20your%20home%20happy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrees%20have%20been%20the%20best%20friends%20of%20humans%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20time.%20From%20giving%20us%20food%20to%20shelter%20under%20its%20shade%2C%20trees%20are%20something%20that%20the%20architects%20advise%20to%20have%20around%20the%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20emphasise%20enough%20the%20need%20and%20importance%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348074%2Fsustainable-home-wayanad-kerala-george-ramapuram-earthitects-hillside-jungle-home-nature%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20trees%20around%20your%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20bring%20in%20shade%2C%20and%20wind%20and%20moderate%20the%20temperature%20around%20them.%20Plant%20as%20many%20trees%20as%20you%20can%20around%20your%20home%20and%20try%20to%20incorporate%20the%20existing%20ones%20in%20the%20design.%20Trust%20me%2C%20they%20are%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lifesaver%20in%20the%20heat%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20George%20Ramapuran%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20sustainable%20design%20firm%2C%20Eartitects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20built%20numerous%20estates%20around%20the%20theme%20of%20sustainability%20and%20nature%20conservation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgreeing%20with%20George%2C%20Shipra%20also%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20greenery%20to%20keep%20the%20heat%20at%20bay.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20constructing%20the%20home%2C%20you%20can%20always%20look%20at%20the%20region-specific%20trees%20and%20plant%20them%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20your%20home%20will%20have%20verandas%20and%20windows.%20This%20will%20ensure%20shade%20in%20those%20areas%20and%20also%20will%20help%20in%20better%20wind%20circulation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Architects%20suggest%20planting%20trees%20around%20the%20house%20to%20increase%20shade%20and%20reduce%20temperatures.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-1-1-1694786484-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330098%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArchitects%20suggest%20planting%20trees%20around%20the%20house%20to%20increase%20shade%20and%20reduce%20temperatures.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDirection%20of%20the%20wind%20and%20sun%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20wind%20and%20sun%20is%20very%20important%20while%20constructing%20your%20home.%20%E2%80%9CPlanning%20is%20crucial%20when%20constructing%20a%20house.%20The%20western%20sun%20can%20be%20harsh%2C%20while%20the%20southern%20exposure%20brings%20in%20heat.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20build%20verandas%20on%20these%20sides%20of%20the%20house%20to%20help%20filter%20the%20sunlight%20and%20reduce%20the%20heat%20entering%20the%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20advises%20George.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20include%20things%20like%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ejaalis%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(lattice)%20and%20smaller%20openings%2C%20other%20than%20windows%20and%20verandahs%2C%20advises%20Shirpa.%20Samira%2C%20too%2C%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejaali%20%3C%2Fem%3Estructures%20to%20increase%20more%20wind%20and%20natural%20light%20inside%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShipra%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20roof%2C%20you%20could%20consider%20making%20it%20slanting%20instead.%20While%20modern%20designs%20do%20not%20support%20it%2C%20such%20roofs%20are%20really%20good%20for%20homes.%20They%20bring%20in%20more%20shade%20in%20the%20house%2C%20they%20look%20authentic%20and%20the%20sun%20is%20never%20hitting%20the%20entire%20roof%20at%20one%20time.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENatural%20materials%20make%20a%20cooler%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20materials%2C%20the%20three%20architects%20agree%20that%20using%20natural%20materials%20can%20bring%20down%20the%20temperatures%20significantly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStudy%20the%20area%20well%20before%20you%20start%20constructing%20your%20home.%20By%20knowing%20the%20area%20well%2C%20you%20can%20find%20natural%20and%20traditional%20materials%20to%20build%20your%20home.%20Mangalore%20tiles%20are%20something%20that%20I%20recommend%20to%20all%20my%20clients.%20These%20tiles%20are%20very%20durable%20and%20breathable.%20A%20Mangalore%20tiled%20roof%20is%20not%20concrete%20and%20has%20space%20for%20cross%20ventilation%20letting%20the%20house%20breathe%2C%E2%80%9D%20George%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20materials%20such%20as%20wood%20and%20stones%20for%20construction%20instead%20of%20cement%20can%20also%20do%20wonders%20for%20the%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAgain%2C%20I%20would%20emphasise%20the%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348313%2Falwar-zero-cement-sustainable-home-rainwater-harvesting-neem-jaggery-built-by-shipra-singhania%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20materials%20such%20as%20mud%2C%20straw%20and%20lime%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20make%20homes.%20Mud%20is%20a%20natural%20coolant%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20turning%20towards%20mud%20homes.%20Additionally%2C%20using%20lime%20on%20the%20floor%20or%20the%20walls%20can%20also%20help%20you%20bring%20down%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20house%20significantly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shipra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20existing%20apartments%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20home%20that%20is%20already%20constructed%20and%20has%20no%20scope%20for%20reconstruction%2C%20there%20are%20some%20%3Cem%3Ejugaads%20(quick%20fixes)%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20these%20architects%20have%20suggested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c